Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:06.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:19.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:21.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:27.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:34.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,又做噩夢了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:43.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:45.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:47.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...這是在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.60,0:00:48.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:50.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,當盲目的群羊所聚集的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:57.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,燃起熊熊火柱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:00.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,乃是天崩之時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:03.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快去 趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:09.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危險?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:12.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道...卡思嘉出事了?
Comment: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:07.42,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/-------START-------/
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:10.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,冬之精靈 宛如雪花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,輕輕地從天空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:18.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,像棉花般飄落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:20.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住一看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:24.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:27.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我抓到一個不得了的東西 里基特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是妖怪板栗仔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:36.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 長高一點了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:43.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,里基特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:46.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你回來啦 艾莉加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,健壯了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:52.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,差點沒認出你來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯 你還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:58.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兩年音訊全無呢 到底去了哪為何沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 里基特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,先不敘舊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉她...沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:07.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉她不見了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...怎麼回事 里基特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:16.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為何會這樣 什麼時候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:19.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:31.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我帶了姐姐出去採集果實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是一個月前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:36.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也是沒有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:39.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為長期在礦洞生活 卡思嘉相當消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:42.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,幾乎都不怎麼吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉加實在是看不下去就帶她出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:50.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等我察覺到的時候 姐姐已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:53.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,里基特 那你為何還在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不去找卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她什麼情況你很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯你個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:01.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把姐姐丟在一邊兩年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:06.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自己卻不知死到哪裏去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也不懂里基特是什麼心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他有去找過找了無數遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,完全可以一去不回的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 里基特還是回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:20.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回到了這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我有不能走的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得人睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:30.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,高特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,染上瘟疫了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:37.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那麼高級
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:39.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是天年 天年已到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:43.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 囉囉嗦嗦地問你話我也嫌麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看看你的劍跟義肢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:52.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卷刃 生銹 變形
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:57.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你在廢寢忘食地斬妖除魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,瘋狂地廝殺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不讓自己神志清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:03.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,否則便活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:10.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兩年前 當里基特把身負重傷的你們帶來這裏時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:13.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你們身上發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:16.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但看到隨後而來的那個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總算可以想像並不是什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 報仇? 血債血償?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你不覺得這是在逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:29.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,逃到報仇雪恨的戰鬥之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨這種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:37.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是無法面對悲傷之人逃避的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:43.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,復仇就如同將生銹的劍沒在血泊中去磨鋒利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,越磨越生銹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:46.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,越是生銹就越要磨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:52.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到最後只剩下一團銹粉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:55.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不會懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:02.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種舒適的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:07.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即將不留任何遺憾地逝去的你是不會懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:09.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有誰能懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人能懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:16.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一個不剩地!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:19.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何先兆地!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:21.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,突如其來地!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,毫不講理地!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:25.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如同螻蟻一般!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在一無所知的情形下!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬間就...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:34.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我心中 他們都是無可替代的存在!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:40.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但你卻拋下那無可替代之人 獨自離去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兩年前的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:47.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你拋下那個從苦難中被救出來的最後一個無可替代之人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:50.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獨自離去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你獨自一人...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:59.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...逃進了用仇恨來燃燒自己的復仇行為中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:00.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拋下那位姑娘 獨自離去的你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:08.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有資格說「為同伴報仇」這句話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在關鍵時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然跑去復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:17.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是一柄出鞘的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有著無數卷刃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,血淋淋而快要生銹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有了致命龜裂...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...行將折斷的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:34.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看 那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:39.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:40.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:43.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了讓自己安心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用我鍛造的劍代替他們的墓碑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也不是真的在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想必在數量上也差得很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:53.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,戰場上經常這樣幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:56.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兩年...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一段足以讓人改變的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我深陷仇恨這段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,里基特建立了劍塚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他接受了同伴的死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:06.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為之哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後找到新的生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:12.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,憑著他獨特的堅強意志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:18.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即使知道這裏很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但黑暗中沒有劍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何都睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:27.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...我這輩子都不可能在夜晚安睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:32.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你獨自離去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:35.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你獨自一人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:38.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...逃進了用仇恨來燃燒自己的復仇行為中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:53.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:55.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是無法逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:10:01.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,烙在這右眼裏最後的恐懼  憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:06.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這紫黑色的火焰絶對不能贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,既然不能贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:10.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,既然無法逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:13.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就只能讓它燃燒自己 燃燒敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你要繼續浴血奮戰!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續殺戮!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:22.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續嗜血!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,孤獨終老!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:34.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拋下處於那種狀況下的她獨自離去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:36.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今還能說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:40.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把等同鷹之團的卡思嘉拋在一邊的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:43.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至沒有資格說為同伴報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:46.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是前突擊隊長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:48.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道究竟是因為夢想或是其他原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:51.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總之他是為了自己而離開的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我們最艱難的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他不在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:58.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這種傢伙 怎能讓人將之稱為同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:01.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經脫團了肥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有理由讓你那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,帶她走吧 即便是硬來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:07.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這次也一定要帶她走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,否則那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:13.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你要為自己奮戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:14.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,必須離開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獨自一人也必須離開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:23.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很早之前 從那時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我就沒有那個資格了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我自己挑起的戰爭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,確實這不是我想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:36.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但至少並沒有為任何人所迫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是我自己挑起的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:40.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:42.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些日子的篝火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還在燃燒著我的胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:03.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不正是這最後餘下的細微篝火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:12.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在最後一刻阻止我被黑色火焰吞噬的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...又重蹈覆轍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快 趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:34.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不會再失去她!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:57.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:00.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你不是睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 我是睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我怕那樣睡著的話會被吃掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:04.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:05.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:08.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆幫義肢加上鑽頭和切割機升級吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 這個太...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:14.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是鞋店小精靈而是鐵匠小精靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:16.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅 你那副樣子!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:19.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事我必須要做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:20.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太魯莽了 讓我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:24.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉加就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:25.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:28.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是我親生女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:32.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是在戰事中失去家人的戰爭孤兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:37.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她 只知道打鐵的我才有個人樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:43.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 死的時候還是一個人...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...獨自上路為好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:55.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別變成我這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:13.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,新的鎧甲如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:15.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是師傅幫你準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:21.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 使用了火藥的新武器和新式改良弩炮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:24.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不必特地組裝也能馬上在緊急光頭使用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近被稱為聖地的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有什麼頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聖地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:34.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裏朝東北走三天左右
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:39.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有一個叫聖阿爾比安寺院的古修道院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人稱判罪塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:42.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,判罪塔...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在那裏住滿了難民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:46.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,據說似乎有邪教徒混在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以法王廳要派遣異端審問官過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:52.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,舉行所謂的魔女審判
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:55.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但你為什麼要問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:56.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:15:00.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為卡思嘉在那的可能性很低
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:01.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我有根據
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:04.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然可以說是溺水者的最後一根救命稻草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:05.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 現在只有相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:06.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不明白是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:13.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉是個什麼樣的女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:15.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:20.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一定要平安歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:25.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,高特 你是個好鐵匠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,歸來之日再麻煩你!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:28.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴啦 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:30.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 不躺著可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:35.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕這次就是與你今生的永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:40.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 總比兩眼淚汪汪地訣別要好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:44.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,像那般朝著某個目標狂奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:47.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總會有路旁的風景被忽略
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:50.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是不如意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:52.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是生還是死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:07.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺像是在民族大遷徙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,瘟疫加饑荒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上庫夏的大舉入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說首都溫達姆在國王駕崩之際
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:15.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被人乘虛而入佔領了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:19.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,下任女王夏洛特公主以及以倚之為首的大部分家臣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,目前下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:24.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是屋漏偏逢連夜雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,注意言辭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:26.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,假若是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在要前往的阿爾比安修道院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是法王廳的直轄領地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:33.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但距離米特蘭國境很近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:37.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,庫夏是我們教廷勢力圈的共同敵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:40.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是悠哉悠哉地進行異端審問儀式的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若有什麼異常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:45.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法王廳應該會傳來新的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:49.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前我們只要默默完成任務就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:49.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞大人的心情比平常更糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:04.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒...沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:06.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要胡思亂想!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那不可能是真的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼會做出那種...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:14.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是幻覺 是噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:17.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在要集中精神執行護送異端審問官的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:21.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便神明吝於在此身展示神蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:24.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要貫徹信仰就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:27.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你離神明十萬八千里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:29.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是心情不好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不是我的幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說可能有點過分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:43.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對法爾納塞團長而言黑色劍士的擔子太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:48.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅以追究她責任的形式解除其緝捕黑色劍士的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:52.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且新的任務居然是護衛那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,心情當然不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:55.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:56.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的馬車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:00.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 以為自己是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:02.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,噓 別亂說話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是異端審問官的馬車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:08.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看 高高褂起的紅色車輪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:12.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那相當於是「血聖書」摩茲古斯的旗號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:14.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個「血聖書」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:18.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...車輪碾刑 刺刑 水刑 火刑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:21.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被那個傢伙判以極刑的少說也有500人以上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:24.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎在拷問過程中死掉的人 更是多達數倍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,相當遭人恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,敵襲?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧 摩茲古斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:38.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我兒子的仇!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:39.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我女兒的仇!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:40.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,納命來!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被難民擋著過不去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兩側被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,滾出來 摩茲古斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:53.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:54.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:05.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:09.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:13.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神尊崇沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:16.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩茲古斯大人 您不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:19.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,萬分抱歉 是我們的疏忽 太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:22.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞團長 抬起頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:25.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神對神職人員是寬容的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:30.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,反而是法王廳方面的人沒有死傷真是萬幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是神的庇護啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:34.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,您說的話實在是不敢擔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:36.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,今後我們會更加努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 這些人是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:42.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是貧僧的手下 專門負責拷問
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,經過嚴格的鍛鐮和任務考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:46.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有鋼鐵般的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:49.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使得他們在任何時候能派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是令人安心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:58.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你們為何要襲擊我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:19:59.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是復仇!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:01.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你燒死了我們全村的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:04.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,汙衊是我們村是邪教徒村
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:09.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,貧僧只是遵從神的教旨做出公正判決
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是因為碰上饑荒 糧食見底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:15.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,才申請暫時停止向寺院上交什一稅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:16.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但你們卻單方面地...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:17.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天誅!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:20.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你會遭報應的!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:21.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天誅...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天誅?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎容得你說天誅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:30.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的行止不端之徒!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:33.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,身為向僧侶出手的叛教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:36.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然說什麼天誅!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就憑你們這群鼠輩?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 在這片大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我們法王廳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:46.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,決不允許任何個人或組織擁有神之代言人的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:48.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞團長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:49.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:54.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為 該對他們判以什麼刑罰才合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:58.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妄圖弒僧之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:21:01.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,通常判處火刑或車輪碾刑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:05.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是光榮的聖鐵鎖騎士團團長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是見多識廣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:11.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就在這裏進行簡單的判法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:12.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,判決如下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.39,0:21:16.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,判處所有被告車輪碾刑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:19.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放過我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:22.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:31.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:45.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:47.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:50.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:53.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別 你會被牽連的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 姑娘 你是他的同夥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:58.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 她是無辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦 小心把你也...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 原來是瘋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:06.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,給我走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:07.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,主啊 請大發慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:08.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:10.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫露加
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:11.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:14.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還真是可怕的景象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:15.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,令人作嘔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:19.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看那種景象只會令人噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:20.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.37,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,為我家人報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.37,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼公正
